title: Age of Mythology Gold (Mac/Intel)
description:
Age of Mythology: The Titians Expansion (Mac/Intel) Tested on Mavericks 10.9

I want to share one of my favorites.

This game was fixed to 1440X900 DON'T change the resolution in game options.

If you have another resolution and want to improve:

1.- Right click Application.
2.- "Show Package Content".
3.- Click Wineskin.app.
4.- "Advanced".
5.- On "EXE Flags" change "xres" and "yres"

Example.

Monitor 1920 X 1080

xres=1920 yres=1080 

Comment anything about this game and more important SSSEEEEEDDDDD!

Thanks.
